      Here's how different situations typically play out for international students in the Netherlands:
    </p>

    <div class="grid md:grid-cols-2 gap-6">
      <div class="border border-neutral-200 rounded-lg p-6">
        <h3 class="font-semibold text-neutral-900 mb-2">Master's Student from India, Not Working</h3>
        <p class="text-neutral-600 mb-4">1-year MSc at TU Delft, focused on studies.</p>
        <p class="text-green-700 font-medium">✓ Uses AON Student Insurance (€45/month). Registered with local huisarts. Got sick once—GP visit was covered, prescriptions covered. Simple and affordable. Very satisfied.</p>
